{"tid":1635522,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[大家睇清楚] 公眾地方蒙面係無犯法","createTime":"2019-10-07T13:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:14:23.000Z","uid":127532,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"24db0e2c2bb886545dd79e5f32dd7108518295d8","tid":1635522,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"有律師已經講過，公眾地方蒙面係無犯法，請大家睇清楚條例<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">任何人不得在身處以下活動時，使用相當可能阻止識辨身分的蒙面物品<br />\na) 非法集結 b) 未經批准集結 c) 公眾集會 d) 公眾遊行</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以你平時搭車、行街、食飯其實係可以蒙面</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不過警察係有權要求你除低面罩，否則可以拉你，但只要你合作除俾佢睇就唔駛怕<br />\n<br />\n我在此呼籲全港市民由聽日開始戴口罩出街，以示抗議！<br />\n呢個活動無成本，風險極低，希望大家齊心去做<br />\n<br />\n條例可以睇呢度︰<a href=\"https://www.sb.gov.hk/chi/antimask/regulation.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sb.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fantimask%2Fregulation.htm&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nCwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=c7603081\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sb.gov.hk/chi/antimask/regulation.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e7232110463f48cd514359dad8ecc808daa6909d","tid":1635522,"uid":127532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"求幫推，有好多人因為怕犯法唔敢戴"},{"pid":"4bf284c6f2435b89f209f73524d9644d91d1e0ad","tid":1635522,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ded41ffeb5a8b5719ebce0cf0a6a97ade399e8d","tid":1635522,"uid":127532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:54:42.000Z","msg":"跪求和理非嚮應<br />\n百萬人戴口罩既相一定又上到國際新聞"},{"pid":"504a5ef93514e5fa31271dedf603641245ec8909","tid":1635522,"uid":259963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:55:27.000Z","msg":"早幾日有個呀爸帶住個3歲大嘅仔落街都比狗兇鳩話佢地非法集結啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zOMHk1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzOMHk1N.png&h=649b24fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">私了一定要爆春袋</span><br />\n仲要唔致命（左膠大愛）<br />\n<br />\n一路叫唔好打頭一路大大力錫佢春袋<br />\n個畫面正到諗起都想打個飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你諗下如果你係藍絲<br />\n比人私了打爆頭壯烈d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係比人私了爆春袋搞笑d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通大大聲係記者鏡頭面前話比人爆袋咩？<br />\n有力講都無面講啦"},{"pid":"167e4329d6d12affd74959da4cb048f78391c401","tid":1635522,"uid":17781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"重點唔係入唔入罪，係黑警鍾意就拉你番去打到斷手斷腳先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c1984b5b7b40096ef499cdb90756fede285100","tid":1635522,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"重點唔係蒙面法<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而係緊急法</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n講咗咁耐都未L明既?"},{"pid":"b731e2737a643f1489bbe743e0197610ba1848ad","tid":1635522,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"我想要一幅全城戴口罩既相做生日禮物呀<br />\n香港人可唔可以送俾我？"},{"pid":"e1eefafacb6a7c0162032351f4608374fd849351","tid":1635522,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85c1984b5b7b40096ef499cdb90756fede285100","tid":1635522,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"重點唔係蒙面法<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而係緊急法</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n講咗咁耐都未L明既?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"我知呀，咁你點反緊急法呀<br />\n依家咪通過反蒙面法黎表達我地反緊急法囉"},{"pid":"4e2b0dadb841feefcb1d3f9438fc58579e57f2e9","tid":1635522,"uid":131125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13: